728063f-a.title: Queens: Sutphin Boulevard - 109th Avenue
728063f-a.text:
Sutphin Boulevard, east side, between 109th Avenue and Arlington Torrace, showing the residence of the priests of St. Joseph's Roman Catholic Church, partially seen on the left.
P. L. Sperr  March 30.1932

728064f-a.title: Queens: Sutphin Boulevard - 109th Avenue
728064f-a.text:
Sutphin Boulevard, east side, between 109th Avenue and Arlington Terrace, showing an old private mansion in rear of St. Josephs Roman Catholic Church. It was for a time the
Church rectory.
March 30, 1932
P. L. Sperr
